==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blacks
<hw>Blacks</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
name of a kind of in used in copperplate printing, prepared from the
charred husks of the grape, and residue of the wine press.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Soot flying in the air.</def>
<mark>[Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Black garments, etc. See <er>Black</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, 4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blacksalter</ent>⟦br⟧
